{"data":{"page":{"id":"9632f5c9-17bf-561e-9388-d085c0b2b9d8","html":"<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5bad5320cd27e263ebbe3fc3bac47713/877ff/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/5bad5320cd27e263ebbe3fc3bac47713/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5bad5320cd27e263ebbe3fc3bac47713/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/5bad5320cd27e263ebbe3fc3bac47713/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>During my tenure at <a href=\"http://www.wcrs.com\">WCRS</a>, I worked on an HTML5 prototype for <a href=\"https://www.mini.co.uk\">MINI</a> that uses the webcam to track the motion of the user’s eyes.</p>\n<p>In this particular application of the technology, the user had to stare for as long as posible without blinking the eyes until the meter reaches the top.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/733e2898cec81415fe1376503d5f24f6/e46a3/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1020px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-i